---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import AgencyApplyForm from '../components/AgencyApplyForm.astro';
---

<Layout title="For Agencies | MANGO Agency" activeNav="for-agencies" lang="en" transparentTop={true}>

  <!-- 1. HERO -->
  <section class="relative h-screen -mt-16 w-full overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center bg-no-repeat" style="background-image: url('/assets/hero-agencies-v3.png');"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-black/80 via-black/60 to-black/20"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none" style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse 320px 220px at 96% 88%, rgba(0,0,0,0.55), transparent 70%);"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center">
      <div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 w-full">
        <div class="max-w-[620px] flex flex-col gap-6">
          <span class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-[0.25em] uppercase text-white/60">For agencies</span>
          <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-black text-white tracking-tight leading-[1.05] whitespace-nowrap">
            Built for OnlyFans agencies
          </h1>
          <p class="text-white/85 text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed">
            We handle chatting and monetization so you can focus on traffic and growth &mdash; without building the team yourself.
          </p>
          <div class="border-l-2 border-white/50 pl-5 text-sm md:text-base text-white/70 leading-snug">
            <p>You keep the model, the brand, and the relationship.</p>
            <p>We increase the revenue.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-2">
            <a href="#agency-apply" class="inline-block bg-accent text-black font-bold px-8 py-4 rounded-xl text-sm tracking-wide hover:brightness-95 transition-all shadow-lg">
              Apply now
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 2. PROBLEM (BLACK) -->
  <section class="py-32 md:py-40 bg-black text-white">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 flex flex-col gap-10">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black tracking-tight leading-[1.1]">
        Most agencies don&rsquo;t have a growth problem <span class="text-white/60">&mdash; they have a monetization problem.</span>
      </h2>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 text-xl md:text-2xl font-semibold text-white/80 border-l-2 border-white/30 pl-6">
        <p>You can get models.</p>
        <p>You can get traffic.</p>
        <p class="text-white">But revenue per model is inconsistent.</p>
      </div>
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-white leading-snug mt-4">
        Chatting is where most of the money is made <span class="text-white/60">&mdash; and where most agencies lose it.</span>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 3. SOLUTION (WHITE) -->
  <section class="py-32 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-on-surface tracking-tight leading-[1.1] mb-14 max-w-3xl">
        We become your monetization system.
      </h2>
      <ul class="flex flex-col gap-5 mb-14 max-w-3xl">
        {[
          'Dedicated chatters assigned per model — trained to match tone, personality, and boundaries.',
          'Structured sales flows (warm-up → engagement → upsell → retention), not random chatting.',
          'Daily tracking of revenue, conversion, and spender behavior.',
          'Weekly performance reviews with clear adjustments and improvements.',
          'Internal QA system to maintain consistency and avoid revenue leaks.',
        ].map(item => (
          <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary flex-shrink-0 mt-1" style="font-size:22px;font-variation-settings:'FILL' 1;">check_circle</span>
            <p class="text-on-surface text-lg leading-relaxed">{item}</p>
          </li>
        ))}
      </ul>
      <div class="border-t border-outline-variant/30 pt-10 max-w-3xl">
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-on-surface font-semibold leading-snug">This is not outsourcing.</p>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-on-surface-variant font-semibold leading-snug mt-1">This is a structured revenue system integrated into your agency.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 4. HOW IT WORKS (SURFACE) -->
  <section class="py-32 bg-surface">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-on-surface tracking-tight leading-[1.1] mb-16 max-w-3xl">How it works.</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-5">
        {[
          { num: '01', title: 'Integration', text: 'We connect with your current setup and understand each model\u2019s positioning, pricing, and audience.' },
          { num: '02', title: 'Setup', text: 'We build the chatting structure, sales flows, and assign dedicated chatters per model.' },
          { num: '03', title: 'Execution', text: 'We handle daily conversations, upsells, retention, and fan segmentation.' },
          { num: '04', title: 'Optimization', text: 'We analyze performance weekly and continuously improve conversion and revenue per fan.' },
        ].map(step => (
          <div class="bg-surface-container-lowest p-10 md:p-12 rounded-2xl border border-outline-variant/20 flex flex-col gap-5">
            <span class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-black text-outline-variant/40 leading-none">{step.num}</span>
            <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-black text-on-surface tracking-tight">{step.title}</h3>
            <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-base leading-relaxed">{step.text}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 5. DIFFERENTIATION (BLACK) -->
  <section class="py-32 md:py-40 bg-black text-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black tracking-tight leading-[1.05] mb-14 max-w-4xl">
        Why top agencies work with us.
      </h2>
      <ul class="flex flex-col gap-5 mb-14 max-w-3xl">
        {[
          'Dedicated chatters per model — trained, monitored, and optimized as part of a structured system.',
          'We track real performance metrics: revenue per fan, conversion rates, and spender behavior.',
          'Every conversation follows a defined sales structure — not guesswork or random chatting.',
          'We plug into your operation without disrupting your workflows or model relationships.',
          'Built to scale across multiple models without losing consistency or control.',
        ].map(item => (
          <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-white flex-shrink-0 mt-1" style="font-size:22px;font-variation-settings:'FILL' 1;">check_circle</span>
            <p class="text-white/85 text-lg leading-relaxed">{item}</p>
          </li>
        ))}
      </ul>
      <div class="border-t border-white/20 pt-10 max-w-3xl">
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-white/60 font-semibold leading-snug">Most agencies grow accounts.</p>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-white font-bold leading-snug mt-1">We turn them into predictable revenue systems.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 6. POSITIONING (WHITE) -->
  <section class="py-32 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 flex flex-col gap-10">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-on-surface tracking-tight leading-[1.1]">Built for agencies ready to scale.</h2>
      <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed max-w-3xl">
        We don&rsquo;t work with early-stage or low-traffic accounts. We partner with agencies that:
      </p>
      <ul class="flex flex-col gap-4 max-w-3xl">
        {[
          'Have active models generating daily traffic.',
          'Already produce consistent monthly revenue.',
          'Want to increase revenue per model, not just grow accounts.',
        ].map(item => (
          <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary flex-shrink-0 mt-1" style="font-size:22px;font-variation-settings:'FILL' 1;">check_circle</span>
            <p class="text-on-surface text-lg leading-relaxed">{item}</p>
          </li>
        ))}
      </ul>
      <div class="border-t border-outline-variant/30 pt-10 max-w-3xl">
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-on-surface font-bold leading-snug">If your models are already moving, we&rsquo;ll scale them.</p>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-on-surface-variant font-semibold leading-snug mt-1">If not, we&rsquo;re not the right fit.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 7. FAQ (SURFACE) -->
  <section class="py-32 bg-surface">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-on-surface tracking-tight leading-[1.1] mb-14">Frequently asked questions.</h2>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
        {[
          {
            q: 'Do you work directly with my models?',
            a: 'No. We operate as your backend system. You keep full ownership of the relationship, the brand, and the communication. We simply handle monetization behind the scenes.',
          },
          {
            q: 'Will my models notice the difference?',
            a: 'No. Everything is adapted to each model\u2019s tone, personality, and boundaries. From the outside, nothing changes. From the inside, revenue improves.',
          },
          {
            q: 'How do you ensure quality in chatting?',
            a: 'We use structured systems, not guesswork: dedicated chatters per model, internal QA and monitoring, performance tracking per chatter, and continuous optimization.',
          },
          {
            q: 'How fast can we start?',
            a: 'Once aligned, setup can be completed in 24 hours and we start optimizing immediately.',
          },
          {
            q: 'How do you get paid?',
            a: 'Performance-based. Each setup is different depending on your models, current revenue, and structure. We only make money if your revenue increases \u2014 that\u2019s how we stay aligned.',
          },
          {
            q: 'Why work with you instead of building this in-house?',
            a: 'You can. But it requires time, hiring, training, management, and constant optimization. We give you a system that already works \u2014 without the operational complexity.',
          },
        ].map(faq => (
          <details class="bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-2xl group border border-outline-variant/20">
            <summary class="p-8 flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer list-none select-none">
              <span class="font-semibold text-on-surface text-base md:text-lg pr-6">{faq.q}</span>
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined expand-icon text-on-surface-variant flex-shrink-0 transition-transform duration-300">add</span>
            </summary>
            <div class="px-8 pb-8 text-on-surface-variant text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed">{faq.a}</div>
          </details>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 8. AGENCY APPLICATION FORM -->
  <AgencyApplyForm lang="en" />

</Layout>
